h2(#description). Description


This plugin is used by other plugins to highlight source code. It is used, for example, by {plugin:
Tag/IncludeFile}.

The available languages for syntax highlighting depend on the version of coderay you have installed.


h2(#caveat). Caveat


This plugin is only available if you have installed the
"coderay":http://coderay.rubychan.de/ library. The preferred way to do this is via
Rubygems:

  gem install coderay
